me.hyperperform.reporting.algorithm

Interface Algorithm

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultimediaAlgorithm, StandardAlgorithm, WebDeveloperAlgorithm

    public interface Algorithm
    Algorithm interface forms part of the Strategy design pattern. The Algorithms are used to calculate performance scores. This interface is the Strategy component of the design pattern, any realizations of this interface with be the ConcreteStrategy. Hyper-perform Group: CodusMaximus Date: 2016/08/19 Feature: Algorithm Strategy
